QuestData.Title: To the... Past?
QuestData.Description:
It is regrettable that we could not stabilize Chronormu, but there is another potential location where we may be able to catch her and bring an end to her fall through time.
<Nozdormu frowns.>
The glimpses of this timeline past are... strange. Even among some of the visions I have witnessed in my life.
Be on your guard, $n. I am uncertain what you will face, but it is powerful and... oddly familiar.
QuestData.LogDescription: Take the portal and meet with Andantenormu in Azmerloth.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Take the portal and meet with Andantenormu in Azmerloth.
QuestData.RewardText: Whatever I expected... This is not it.
